@~/.local/share/agent-skills/AGENTS.md

Skills are available at ~/.local/share/agent-skills

When using skills, always:
1. Activate the virtual environment: `cd ~/.local/share/agent-skills && source .venv/bin/activate`
2. Run scripts from the agent-skills directory
3. Reference skill documentation with `@~/.local/share/agent-skills/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md`
